		"description": "API testing suite for https://fakestoreapi.com\n\nCoverage: Auth, Products, Carts, Users (full CRUD), negative cases, JSON Schema validation (AJV), response-time and variable chaining.\n\nNOTE: FakeStoreAPI is a *fake* backend. POST/PUT/PATCH/DELETE return a simulated response (echo + id) and do NOT persist data. Tests assert on the simulated response shape, not on later retrieval.",
